Package com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.base.main

Contains an entry point of the Application.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    App
    Represents refined Application logic, that is logic without processing of command-line arguments and some other routines that need to be done before the pure Application logic can be executed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuiceLocator
    Allows to conveniently locate published instances of GuiceModule.
    LockFileWriter
    Provides ability to write to the Lock File.
    Main
    Provides Java Main.main(String[]) method.
    Main.MainGuiceModule
    This GuiceModule is aware of the following: @Singleton ApplicationConfig @Singleton ConfigLocator @Singleton LockFileWriter
    Std
    Provides methods for printing to System.out and System.err that append some useful information to printed strings.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ApplicationConfigPropertyName
    Represents names of properties that are specified by the Application Config.
    Std.StreamType
    Represents type of a standard stream.
